{"tid":845106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歸邊]  美墨加協議添信心，川普再轟印度、巴西貿易不公","createTime":"2018-10-02T11:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T14:32:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32ce3fc67f83c0627a01b92b01acc8512091c644","tid":845106,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"美墨加協議添信心，川普再轟印度、巴西貿易不公<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E6%B7%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%86%8D%E8%BD%9F%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC-013655018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.stock.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25BD%259F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC-013655018.html&d=MzvXRyIBp%2FgBxpgrfSPzQKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=4667df9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E5%8A%A0%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E6%B7%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%86%8D%E8%BD%9F%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC-013655018.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普在新版北美貿易協議取得歷史性的一勝後，砲口轉向印度與巴西，他甚至批評後者貿易保護手段可能是全球最強硬的。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">路透社報導，川普周一在白宮慶功宴上批評印度貿易政策，關於美國獲不公平對待，他已向印度總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）表達不滿，並獲得調降關稅承諾。 <br />\n<br />\n在批評印度後，川普緊接著抨擊南美第一大國巴西，且砲火更為猛烈，他說巴西貿易政策聲名狼籍，關稅稅率可任意調整，想多重就課多重。 </span><br />\n<br />\n美國是巴西第二大貿易夥伴，僅次於中國。官方數據顯示，巴西與美國去年貿易總額達520億美元，今年前八個月巴西對美國貿易呈現小幅逆差。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Indiatimes.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FIndiatimes.com&d=MzvXRyIBp%2FgBxpgrfSPzQKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=12cb2599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Indiatimes.com</a>報導，川普當日還表示白宮正分別與歐盟、中國、日本與印度就新貿易協議進行談判，並稱<span style=\"color: red;\">印度想討好他心切，態度也最積極。</span>"},{"pid":"4b24a0b01d91cd50338d6e4b90cf74abc1fdbe88","tid":845106,"uid":46896,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"啊侵仆街在咩著數都拎晒，留返啲豬頭骨俾其他國家"},{"pid":"5df9e2cc472a5b23a9db93b32f8e784e377d32a9","tid":845106,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a71df4b48bd3e7a505259a15b55401de4d08ad","tid":845106,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b17f61789cb384aab3d425cb95fde2e55049ec9","tid":845106,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5df9e2cc472a5b23a9db93b32f8e784e377d32a9","tid":845106,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"唔係痴線,係好有計劃咁去做"},{"pid":"a8f71cffb3c6c318fc2c8f6de6982d9e8ff208fb","tid":845106,"uid":39777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"真係重整世界秩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cd2e3b7c77735977d1ab141a477c99358e15b4","tid":845106,"uid":10637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:12:16.000Z","m